data.description: Welcome Home! A rare find!  A Beautiful as-is quaint home in its original beauty.  Once you enter this home, you'll feel the years of love it encompasses.  This 4-sided brick home features 2 bedrooms on the main floor, and a huge beautiful loft with 2 large rooms that runs the length of the home that can certainly be used as bedrooms.  It  has a separate dining room, separate living room, and a small den area.  The front yard yields great open space waiting for your beautiful flowers to be planted.  The backyard is large and level, open for play, your garden and/or your outside entertaining.    This home is nestled among an array of lovely homes in the most preferred and desired zip code area of Atlanta, Dekalb County.  Whether you are a home owner or an investor, you will be delighted to make this home your own. Just waiting for you and your special touch.
